				\begin{document}$$\Omega $$\end{document}Ω denotes the set of all known associated index pairs (i,j) in H and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
