To assess the EMCMDA’s applicability on different datasets, we conducted Global LOOCV and 5-fold CV based on the HMDD v3.0 database38. We acquired 1062 miRNAs, 893 diseases and 35362 known MDAs from the HMDD v3.0 database. In this context, we set the parameters \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
